description:
Cat Quest is a small open world ARPG set in a cute world full of cats and cat puns. 
Slash and dodge enemies while completing quests, dungeons and obtaining new gear.

0.1.0-alpha.description:
Implements a simple AP World for Cat Quest

Includes everything needed to generate a game

0.3.0-alpha.description:
## Changes in this version
- Added options to:
  - change which way you want to get skill upgrades
    - The vanilla way
    - As progressive skills
    - As progressive skillupgrades
    - As progressive magic levels (That will level up all available skills)
  - Several goal options:
    - Main quest
    - Questsanity
    - Max level (Level 99)
    - Max level and Main quest
    - Spellmastery (where all skills need to reach level 10. It works with all skill options too)
  - Include temples as locations
  - include monuments as locations
  - Receive quest rewards or not
- Reworked the entire apworld to be more streamlined and futureproof, including the archipelago.json file

## Learn more about this AP-world
- [Setup guide](https://github.com/Nikkilites/Archipelago-CatQuest/blob/main/worlds/cat_quest/docs/setup_en.md)
- [Info](https://github.com/Nikkilites/Archipelago-CatQuest/blob/main/worlds/cat_quest/docs/en_Cat%20Quest.md)
